		<title><![CDATA[Detect Ransomware]]></title>
		<link>https://annk.info/detect-ransomware/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 31 Mar 2017 03:18:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://annk.info/detect-ransomware/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img alt="ransomware" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-142" data-attachment-id="142" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ransomware" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ransomware.jpeg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ransomware.jpeg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ransomware.jpeg?w=620" data-orig-size="1350,675" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/ransomware/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ransomware.jpeg?w=620" /><br />Mình share cách mà mình tìm ra 1 con virus nào đó bất kỳ đây  là cách cơ bản ko có gì là cao siêu cả nhưng các chú IT phải  nhớ để xài khi hệ thống của các chú bị các chú virus ghé  thăm và dạo này đang HOT chú ransomware tống tính nhằm tống  tiền :p<br /><br /><a name='more'></a><br /><span></span><br />Tìm ra nó để làm gì?<br />+ Tìm rồi send mẫu: hiện giờ trong và ngoài VN đang có khá  nhiều team đang nghiêu cứu từng ngày phân tích các mẫu ransomware  để tìm ra cách giải mã.<br />+ Tìm rồi xóa: tránh tình trạng lây lang trong toàn bộ network<br />3 step thần thánh<br /><ol><li>Kill process – tắt các tiến trình “tào lao”</li><li>Reveal hidden files – hiện các file bị ẩn</li><li>Locate startup location – xác định vị trí (Registry)</li></ol>Trước khi đi vào phân tích từng step mình sẽ đưa ra demo để  các bạn dễ hiểu cũng như dựa vào 1 vài manh mối nhỏ để bạn  dễ dàng xác định được đâu là ransomware.<br /><img alt="17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" data-attachment-id="120" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,540" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457473_10211969883379015_2146478083078273762_n.jpg?w=620" /><img alt="17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" data-attachment-id="122" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />Chúng ta dựa vào các manh mối sau đây<br />+ Time modified của file bị mã hóa: time chỉnh sửa lần cuối  cùng là ngày nào mấy giờ? =&gt; time này thường sẽ trùng với  time mà con ransomware bắt đầu chui zô máy và bèm cái mớ file  data của bạn.<img alt="17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-121" data-attachment-id="121" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n.jpg?w=620?w=225" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="720,960" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498624_10211969883299013_7639469661338218081_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />+ Tên email: manh mối này hên xui phải kết hợp với manh mối time phía trên.<br /><img alt="17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" data-attachment-id="122" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17498534_10211969884779050_6429591469566489321_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />+ Còn 1 cách nữa là các bạn vào Run gõ msconfig, chuyển qua  tab Startup =&gt; list show ra là all những gì sẽ được khởi động  cùng với OS của bạn. Nếu bạn thấy có 1 soft nào là lạ bạn ko  sure là chính bạn đã cài nó vào thì bạn hãy Disabled nó đi  nghĩa là bạn sẽ ko cho phép nó khởi động cùng Win, sau đó bạn  khởi động máy lại.<br /><ul><li>Khi máy đã khởi động xong, bạn lại vào Startup xem lại,  biểu hiện cho thấy nó là virus (trong bài này là ransomware) là  nó sẽ vẫn Enable :p dù lúc nãy bạn Disabled ko cho khởi động  cùng Win nhưng reset máy lại thì nó vẫn đc tự khởi động.</li></ul><img alt="17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-123" data-attachment-id="123" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522995_10211969886459092_6489078724463646752_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />Ok bây giờ mình sẽ đi vào từng step để các bạn hiểu rỏ để sau này có thể ứng dụng vào các trường hợp khác<br /><ol><li>Kill process – xác định tiến trình tào lao :p</li></ol>+ Mở task manager lên bằng Ctrl + Shift + Esc<br />+ Bạn kiểm tra danh sách processes đang chạy, xem thử có process nào có cái tên tào lao mía lao đáng nghi hay ko.<br />+ Process nào mà bạn nghi ngờ thì hãy chuột phải và chọn  Open file location. 1 cửa sổ hiện ra cho ta biết được file đó đang  nằm ở đâu trong máy, bạn rê chuột vào file đó thông tin sẽ  hiện ra trong đó có cái <b>Date created</b>, bạn so sánh với cái <b>time modified</b> của file bị mã hóa. Nếu nó trùng nhau thì tỷ lệ e nó là hung thủ rất cao.<br />+ Sau khi tìm đc vị trí của em nó thì nhớ end process đó  trong task manager đi nhé. Trong tình huống demo thì tên của  process là mouse<br /><img alt="17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-125" data-attachment-id="125" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17522697_10211969886179085_7972902344670797556_n.jpg?w=620" /><br /><ol start="2"><li>Reveal hidden files – hiện các file bị ẩn: step này dùng để  show all file bị ẩn tùy con ransomware mà nó có ẩn trốn hay ko  nên làm thêm bước này để sure là sẽ show all :p</li></ol>+ Vào một thư mục bất kỳ<br />+ Click on “Organize”<br />+ Chọn “Folder and Search Options”<br />+ Chuyển qua tab “View”<br />+ Check “Show hidden files and folders” option<br />+ Uncheck “Hide protected operating system files”<br />+ Click “Apply” và&nbsp; “OK”<br /><ol start="3"><li>Locate startup location – xác định vị trí (Registry)</li></ol>+ Nhấn nút Windows + R, gõ Regedit<br />+ Tìm 1 trong 3 địa chỉ sau<br />+ [HKEY_CURRENT_USERSoftwareMicrosoftWindowsCurrentVersionRun] or<br />+ [HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINESOFTWAREMicrosoftWindowsCurrentVersionRun] or<br />+ HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINESOFTWAREWow6432NodeMicrosoftWindowsCurrentVersionRun]<br /><img alt="17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-126" data-attachment-id="126" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17457516_10211969884859052_717247277436335284_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />+ Sau khi thấy tên em nó thì nhớ xóa đi nhé<br />+ Vào 1 folder bất kỳ, copy past lên thanh địa chỉ những thư  mục sau đây, sau khi kiểm tra ở từng thu mực và xóa các file  virus đi thì coi như xong.<br /><ul><li><b>%AppData%</b></li><li><b>%LocalAppData%</b></li><li><b>%ProgramData%</b></li><li><b>%WinDir%</b></li><li><b>%Temp%</b></li></ul><img alt="17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" data-attachment-id="124" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-description="" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n" data-large-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n.jpg?w=620?w=620" data-medium-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n.jpg?w=620?w=300" data-orig-file="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n.jpg?w=620" data-orig-size="960,541" data-permalink="https://nguyenkan.wordpress.com/2017/03/26/detet-ransomware/17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n/#main" src="https://nguyenkan.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/17362435_10211969884939054_8235347714458772057_n.jpg?w=620" /><br />+ Tại step 1: khi nhấn open file location thì bạn đã biết  chính xác vị trí của file thực thi của ransomware, trước khi  bạn xóa thì hãy nén lại và liên lạc vớ các team support để  được hỗ trợ trước khi xóa nhé.]]></content:encoded>
