		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>Chào các bạn bên mình cung cấp các dịch vụ sau <o:p></o:p><br /><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div style="text-align: center;"><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://chiptroniks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/laptop-repairing-course.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://chiptroniks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/laptop-repairing-course.jpg" data-original-height="280" data-original-width="600" height="149" width="320" /></a></div></div></div><div><br /></div><div><b>Khắc phục xự cố phần mềm:</b><o:p></o:p></div><div style="mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"></div><ul><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Khắc phụ xự cố windows</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Cài mới windows 7/8/8.1/10</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Cài soft theo chuyên ngành như Photoshop, Illutrator, Corel, Accumarker, AutoCad, 3D Max,….</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Cứu dữ liệu</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Xử lý virus</span></li></ul><b>Khắc phục xự cố máy tính bàn (pc):</b><br /><div><o:p></o:p></div><div style="mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; text-indent: -.25in;"></div><ul><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Kiểm tra vệ sinh, tổng quát máy</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Kiểm tra, chẫn đoán tình trạng linh kiện</span></li><li>·<span style="font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Sửa chữa thay thế linh kiện</span></li></ul><div style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l1 level2 lfo2; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;">o<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Mainboard<o:p></o:p></div><div style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l1 level2 lfo2; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;">o<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Ổ cứng (HDD)<o:p></o:p></div><div style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l1 level2 lfo2; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;courier new&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;">o<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font