		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://annk.info/eng-how-to-check-battery-smartphone-2nd/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://i1.wp.com/9to5mac.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2016/10/smartphone-battery-life-2016.png?resize=1600%2C1000&amp;quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;ssl=1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="500" data-original-width="800" height="200" src="https://i1.wp.com/9to5mac.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2016/10/smartphone-battery-life-2016.png?resize=1600%2C1000&amp;quality=82&amp;strip=all&amp;ssl=1" width="320" /></a></div><br /><div style="clear: both;">1 / Charge your phone battery 100% after that</div><div style="clear: both;">2 / Turn on the device in airplane mode,</div><div style="clear: both;">3 / Turn off applications running in the background,</div><div style="clear: both;">4 / Turn on the screen continuously with the highest brightness within 1 hour</div><div style="clear: both;">If the machine is missing</div><div style="clear: both;">+ Over 15% battery, the device may be defective, bottle, ...</div><div style="clear: both;">+ Under 15% battery, the battery is okay</div><div style="clear: both;"><br /></div><div style="clear: both;">p / s: In fact, nobody gives you 100% charge for testing but you can test it by way. After taking the machine please open youtube, the screen is constantly bright, .... running the game in general just use the machine according to the normal needs of 30min to check the battery loss, after using 30min if the machine is too much loss So think again.</div><br /><div style="text-align: left;"></div><br /><div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><br /></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
