		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://annk.info/tool-soi-logonsessions/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Nếu bạn nghĩ rằng khi bạn đăng nhập vào hệ thống chỉ có một phiên đăng nhập hoạt động, tiện ích này sẽ làm bạn ngạc nhiên. Nó liệt kê các phiên đăng nhập hiện đang hoạt động và, nếu bạn chỉ định tùy chọn -p, các quy trình đang chạy trong mỗi phiên.&nbsp;<div style="text-align: center;"><img alt="step3.jpg (626Ã438)" src="https://www.lepide.com/imagesrd/howto/track-user-logon-session-time/step3.jpg" /></div><div style="text-align: center;">Hình ảnh mang tính chất minh họa :p</div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div>https://download.sysinternals.com/files/logonSessions.zip<div><br />Cú pháp: logonsessions [-c[t]] [-p]<br /><br /><div>-c&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Print output as CSV. =&gt; xuất ra file csv<br />-ct&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Print output as tab-delimited values. =&gt; Xuất ra dưới dạng giá trị được phân định bằng tab<br />-p&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; List processes running in logon session. =&gt; Liệt kê các process đang chạy trong phiên đăng nhập</div><div><br /></div><div>Ví dụ:<br /><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; table-layout: auto; width: 662px;"><thead style="box-sizing: inherit;"><tr style="box-sizing: inherit;"><th style="border-width: 0px 0px 1px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; vertical-align: bottom;"><pre style="-webkit-font-smoothing: auto; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400; hyphens: none; line-height: 19px; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; padding: 16px; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal;"><code style="-webkit-font-smoothing: auto; border-radius: 2px; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"><br /></code><code style="-webkit-font-smoothing: auto; border-radius: 2px; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;">C:&gt;logonsessions -p <br /><br />[13] Logon session 00000000:6a6d6160:<br />    User name:    NTDEVmarkruss<br />    Auth package: Kerberos<br />    Logon type:   RemoteInteractive<br />    Session:      1<br />    Sid:          S-1-5-21-397955417-626881126-188441444-3615555<br />    Logon time:   7/2/2015 6:05:31 PM<br />    Logon server: NTDEV-99<br />    DNS Domain:   NTDEV.CORP.MICROSOFT.COM<br />    UPN:          markruss@ntdev.microsoft.com<br />    15368: ProcExp.exe<br />    17528: ProcExp64.exe<br />    13116: cmd.exe<br />    17100: conhost.exe<br />     6716: logonsessions.exe</code><code style="-webkit-font-smoothing: auto; border-radius: 2px; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"><br /></code><code style="-webkit-font-smoothing: auto; border-radius: 2px; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 19px; padding: 0px;"><br /></code></pre></th><th style="border-width: 0px 0px 1px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; vertical-align: bottom;"></th></tr></thead><tbody style="box-sizing: inherit;"><tr style="box-sizing: inherit;"><td style="border-width: 1px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; vertical-align: top;"></td><td style="border-width: 1px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; vertical-align: top;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: inherit;"><td style="border-width: 1px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; vertical-align: top;"></td><td style="border-width: 1px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; vertical-align: top;"></td></tr><tr style="box-sizing: inherit;"><td style="background-color: white; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, SegoeUI, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 12px 16px; vertical-align: top;"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
