		<title><![CDATA[[ENG] How to fix a missing vcruntime140.dll is missing error in Windows]]></title>
		<link>https://annk.info/eng-how-to-fix-a-missing-vcruntime140-dll-is-missing-error-in-windows/</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2020 03:48:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://annk.info/eng-how-to-fix-a-missing-vcruntime140-dll-is-missing-error-in-windows/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">To fix the vcruntime140.dll is missing error in Windows, please follow these steps:</div><ol style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">Go to the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=52685" rel="nofollow noopener" style="background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; outline: none; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank">Microsoft Visual C++ 2015 Redistributable page</a>&nbsp;from Microsoft and click on the&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Download</span>&nbsp;button.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">You will be brought to page where it asks you to select whether you want to download the 32-bit or 64 bit version of Windows. Select the version you need and click the&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Next</span>&nbsp;button. If you are unsure what version you need, you can search google&nbsp;to determine what you need :p&nbsp;</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">The file will now download to your computer. Once downloaded, double-click on the downloaded&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">vc_redist.x64.exe</span>&nbsp;file.&nbsp;</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">The Microsoft Visual C++-2015 Redistributable screen will be displayed and ask you to agree to the license terms and conditions. Put a checkmark in the "I agree" box and then click on the&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Install</span>&nbsp;button.<div style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0px;"><img alt="Microsoft Visual C++-2015 Redistributable" class="b-lazy b-loaded" height="300" src="https://www.bleepstatic.com/images/news/tutorials/windows/d/missing-dlls/api-ms-win-crt-runtime-l1-1-0.dll/visual-c++-2015-redistributable.jpg" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;" width="485" /><figcaption style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Microsoft Visual C++-2015 Redistributable</span></figcaption></figure></div></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">If Windows prompts you to allow the program to make changes or continue, click on the&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Yes&nbsp;</span>or&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Allow</span>&nbsp;button.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">When done, the program will display a message stating that it was successfully installed.<div style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0px;"><img alt="Redistributable Installed" class="b-lazy b-loaded" height="300" src="https://www.bleepstatic.com/images/news/tutorials/windows/d/missing-dlls/api-ms-win-crt-runtime-l1-1-0.dll/success.jpg" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;" width="485" /><figcaption style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Redistributable Installed</span></figcaption></figure></div></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">You can now close the installer.</li></ol><div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">If you already had the DLL installed and it is still showing as missing, you can download the above Redistributable, but this time perform a repair.</div><div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;"><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0px;"><img alt="Perform a Repair" class="b-lazy b-loaded" height="300" src="https://www.bleepstatic.com/images/news/tutorials/windows/d/missing-dlls/api-ms-win-crt-runtime-l1-1-0.dll/repair.jpg" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;" width="485" /><figcaption style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Perform a Repair</span></figcaption></figure></div><div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">You can now try to run the program that previously gave the missing vcruntime140.dll error and it should work again.</div><div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626; font-family: roboto, sans-serif;">bleepingcomputer</span></div>]]></content:encoded>
