		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img class="aligncenter wp-image-495 size-large" src="https://annk.info/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Google-Digital-Garage--1024x336.png" alt="" width="1024" height="336" />

Tết ở nhà làm gì nếu bạn là người hướng "học" phía dưới là vài khoá học mà mình lướt được tại <a href="https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/">Google Digital Garage</a>
<h2>1. Fundamental of Digital Marketing:</h2>
– Time: 40 hours

– Certificate: Yes

– Fee: Free

– Link:https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/course/digital-marketing
<h2>2. Learn Python basics for data analysis</h2>
.– Time: 6 hours– Certificate: Yes– Fee: Free

– Link: https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/course/learn-python-basics-for-data-analysis
<h2>3. Exploring and Preparing your Data with BigQuery</h2>
– Time: 8 hours

– Certificate: Yes

– Fee: Free

– Link: https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/course/preparing-data-bigquery
<h2>4. Data Science Foundations</h2>
– Time: 1.5 hours

– Certificate: Yes

– Fee: Free

– Link: https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/course/data-science-foundations
<h2>5. Data Science with Python</h2>
– Time: 8 hours

– Certificate: yes

– Fee: Free

– Link: https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage/course/data-science-with-python

&nbsp;]]></content:encoded>
